  "title": "Senior Operations Manager $9K - $12K + VB (Waste & Environmental Services)",
  "description": "<p>Lead and manage end-to-end operations, ensuring efficient and\nsustainable waste collection, treatment, recycling, and disposal while driving profitability and customer satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Key Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee daily operations of the waste management facility</li><li>Develop and execute operational and strategic plans</li><li>Manage budgets, costs, KPIs, and financial performance</li><li>Ensure compliance with environmental and safety regulations</li><li>Lead department heads and teams across operations and support functions</li><li>Drive continuous improvement, sustainability, and safety culture</li><li>Handle customer issues and operational escalations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Environmental Science, Engineering, Business or related field (Master’s preferred)</li><li><strong>5+ years’ experience in Waste Management</strong>, including <strong>2+ years in Management</strong></li><li>Strong knowledge of environmental regulations and waste practices</li><li>Proven leadership, budgeting, and operational management skills</li><li>Waste Management Certification is an advantage</li></ul><p><strong>Apply Now:</strong> jeffrey@oaktree.com.sg<br /><strong>Contact:</strong> Jeffrey Chua Kay Hwee<br /><strong>EA License No: 06C4642 | EA Reg No: R1110624</strong></p>",
